    outline: ["Why is Halifax's climate hard on buildings?", "What does salt air do to homes near the harbour?", "How do freeze-thaw cycles damage Halifax properties?", "Heritage home or new build: what should you watch for?", "A season-by-season maintenance checklist for Halifax", "When should you bring in a professional?"],
